<h2>4 · Code It 💻</h2>
<p>Open the IDE at <strong>app.english-coding.co.uk</strong> and write your own program.</p>
<p>Build a <strong>list of dictionaries</strong> called <code>shop</code>, where each item is a dictionary with a <code>"name"</code> key and a <code>"price"</code> key. Put three items in it.</p>
<p>Then <strong>loop over</strong> the shop and print each item's name and price on its own line.</p>
<p>Run it, then write your code and what it printed.</p>
